# CardCheckbox (Momentum) — Momentum guidance (Cursor)

**CardCheckbox** is a **card** that acts as a **checkbox**: click or keyboard toggles **`checked`**, **`role="checkbox"`**, and **`onChange`**. **Multiple** cards in a set can be **checked** at once. **Requires `cardTitle`**. Wrap a group in **`role="group"`** with an **`aria-label`**.

See also: [Card](./card.mdc), [CardRadio](./cardradio.mdc), [Checkbox](./checkbox.mdc).

Browse the [Momentum Components catalog](https://momentum.design/en/components/) for naming; Storybook documents props and examples. Reference: [Storybook — CardCheckbox / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-cardcheckbox--docs). Optional: [Example](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/story/components-card-cardcheckbox--example).

---

## Import

Requires <ThemeProvider> and <IconProvider> ancestors. See setup.mdc.

```jsx
import { CardCheckbox, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";
```

---

## What it is

- **`checked`:** boolean (default **`false`**).  
- **`selectionType`:** `check` (check icon) or `checkbox` (**StaticCheckbox** visuals).  
- **Events:** **`onChange`**, **`onClick`**, focus/key handlers as in Storybook.  
- **No nested interactives** in body/footer slots.  
- **`disabled`** when applicable.  
- Same **card** visuals as **Card** (`variant`, `orientation`, `imageSrc`, …) via shared mixins.

### Defaults (package)

**`checked`** **`false`** unless controlled.

---

## Key props

- **`cardTitle`** (required) · **`checked`**, **`onChange`**, **`selectionType`**, **`disabled`**, plus card surface props (`variant`, `orientation`, `imageSrc`, …)

---

## Example

```jsx
import { CardCheckbox, Text } from "@momentum-design/components/dist/react";


<div role="main">
  <CardCheckbox
    variant="border"
    orientation="vertical"
    cardTitle="Title"
    subtitle="Subtitle"
    imageSrc="https://picsum.photos/seed/momentum-cc/640/360"
    imageAlt="Decorative card image"
    iconName="placeholder-bold"
    selectionType="check"
    titleTagName="span"
    subtitleTagName="span"
  >
    <Text slot="body" tagname="span">
      Supporting description for this selectable card.
    </Text>
  </CardCheckbox>
</div>
```

Align **`onChange`** with your version’s **`detail`** / controlled pattern from Storybook.

---

## Checklist for Cursor prototypes

- [ ] **`ThemeProvider`** + **`IconProvider`** when using **`iconName`**  
- [ ] **`cardTitle`** on every **CardCheckbox**  
- [ ] **Group** container: **`role="group"`** + **`aria-label`**  
- [ ] For **one-of-many** (single choice), use **`CardRadio`** + shared **`name`**, not a checkbox list  

Cross-check [Storybook — CardCheckbox / Docs](https://momentum.design/storybook-static/index.html?path=/docs/components-card-cardcheckbox--docs) and your installed package version.
